Interface HavenOnDemandService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HavenOnDemandServiceImpl

    public interface HavenOnDemandService
    Service which allows arbitrary requests to be made to HP Haven OnDemand

        version - The version of the API
        params - The query parameters sent to the API. These should include a token

        Returns:
